{"title":"黎明","authors":["全哲"],"dates":[{"year":1962,"month":6,"day":19}],"parts":[{"type":"paragraph","text":"黎明"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔朝鲜〕全哲"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"清晨，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我站在首都中心——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"高耸云霄的千里马铜像下，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"激动的心情不能平静。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"心脏的跳动，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛前夕的钟声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"声声传来，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"号唤着出发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"抬头眺望"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"拂晓的苍穹，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"骏马展翅挥膀，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"待命进发。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"啊，千里马！"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你浑身闪烁着，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"国土万民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"热情和力量的光辉。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那奔腾的飞姿，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"你那?喝的吼声，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"是我国人民，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"进军的磅礴气势。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这庄严的阵势，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"仿佛一气跨过六个高地，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"越过世纪，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"迈进到未来的地平线上……"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"曙光透过绵延山林，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"射出万丈光芒；"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"大地沐浴在阳光里，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"发出光彩。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"看，那祖国千里江山："},{"type":"paragraph","text":"铁水沸腾，麦浪起伏，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"棉布川流，煤堆冲天，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"渔业兴旺，高楼遍地——"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"这是屹立在东方，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"日益富裕的社会主义强国。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"前进！千里马，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们勒紧缰绳奔向明天。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"在你那金色的翅膀上空，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"升起了红太阳。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"我们为大地的更大幸福和欢笑，"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"奔向伟大的前程。"},{"type":"paragraph","text":"〔李春镐译〕"}],"comments":[],"comment_pivots":[],"description":"","page_start":6,"page_end":6}